<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<I c="LootActions" i="action" m="interactions.utils.loot" n="loot_WorldEp21_AskAboutWorldLandmarks" s="484456">
  <L n="loot_actions">
    <V t="notification_and_dialog">
      <U n="notification_and_dialog">
        <V n="dialog" t="notification">
          <U n="notification">
            <V n="icon" t="enabled">
              <V n="enabled" t="participant">
                <U n="participant">
                  <L n="participant_type">
                    <E>TargetSim</E>
                  </L>
                </U>
              </V>
            </V>
            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0xB554ACD7<!--String: "Verdemar's town centre holds an ancient challenge for those daring enough to try it. Best to train your sword arm first."--></T>
                  <T>0xA6E892FA<!--String: "An old sailor's tale talks about a sword. It can make its owner the greatest among nobles...but only those who are worthy can obtain it. Are you worthy?"--></T>
                  <T>0x92B6D2E4<!--String: "Adventurers from the south used to tell tales of a strange well. Apparently, it favors tricksters and outcasts. Whatever that means."--></T>
                  <T>0x246AF447<!--String: "That spider well in Dambele...be careful around it. When you talk through the well, the being that answers is certainly a clever one...but also quite the trickster."--></T>
                  <T>0xBF61409F<!--String: "Something worth seeing? Frogs! Of course, it's always frogs. They are everywhere...or at least inside their little log houses. You think frogs are not that special? Well, sometimes appearances can be deceiving."--></T>
                  <T>0x53BDE66D<!--String: "Frogs are different here. At least, a few of them are. Might be of interest to those looking for true love."--></T>
                  <T>0xDF1E61B4<!--String: "Have you heard of Isola del Vero? It's a small, peaceful island in the lake. On there, a strange enchanted object. A mirror, of all things! But what else could it be, in a vain place such as Bellacorde?"--></T>
                  <T>0x5D8F48C9<!--String: "The mirror...it's supposed to show who you are...but do be careful with it: when you stare at it, it stares right back at you. And you never know what that could bring."--></T>
                  <T>0x165BB52C<!--String: "There's this...completely anonymous criminal band, a crew of sorts. We...they tend to hide their treasure chests around Ondarion. Best to leave those chests alone, there can be very fragile shoes inside."--></T>
                  <T>0xE53CF2BD<!--String: "Those Crystal Slippers will give <i>anyone</i> a golden chance at power and love...if you're shallow enough to care about those things."--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
          </U>
        </V>
      </U>
    </V>
    <V t="buff">
      <U n="buff">
        <U n="buff">
          <T n="buff_type">485724<!--Buff: buff_Ep21World_AskCooldown--></T>
        </U>
      </U>
    </V>
  </L>
</I>